data.description: Welcome to 212 Villa Bay Drive, where the coastal vibe of Panama City Beach's Emerald Cove is the setting for this delightful single-story residence. Built in 2020, this four-bedroom, two-bath smart home celebrates the essence of Florida living with understated elegance and thoughtful design. The open floor plan and living areas flow effortlessly. The kitchen has ample preparation and storage space, ready for your culinary adventures. New flooring was recently installed in the walk-in closet and one of the bedrooms. Outside, the deck offers a serene setting for tranquil mornings sipping coffee or relaxing evenings. Located 21 miles from the Northwest Florida Beaches International Airport, 1.7 miles from NAS Panama City, and 18 miles from Tyndall Air Force Base, this home offers a seamless blend of laid-back beach living and convenient access to work and play. The promise of sandy beaches, community spirit, and a wealth of local culture is just around the corner, making every day a blend of relaxation and exploration.This home is an invitation to a more peaceful pace of life, all while staying connected to the pulse of Panama City Beach. It's a place where your time is truly your own, in a community where life's conveniences are never far away. Come and see what it means to live the Florida lifestyle redefined with comfort and ease. Call today to schedule your private tour.
